Class Lass, <br><br>
I remember using the MARS station in Da Nang,right after Christmas 1967.<br><br>
The Lieutenant made me go in and call home cause I hadn't written home in a long time.  <br>
I mean what could I write home about if I couldn't write about what was real and my Ex-wife didn't want to hear it.<br><br>
Thank God you had to say over, I never did and left. I wonder if she's still waiting for me to say over?<br><br>
Thanks Class lass it brought back some memories.<br><br>
OVER<br><br>
Cook
